narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes, I would definitely recommend this class! I'm not sure if we the students put in the right amount of focus and energy to get everything out of it that we wanted, but I do think it was a rewarding and fun class.
Take this class you senior year if you can with Deb. The lessons you learn will travel with you into the world after Yale.
Fantastic way to continue the acting track at Yale with further scene study and ensemble exploration. Deb is just the most wonderful person.
A life class more than a scene study class, but well worth your time.
Take a class with Deb. Period. Do it.
